title: Agent@Home Travel Summit Town Hall Addresses Major Industry Issues
text:
Last updated: 06:53 PM ET, Fri September 18 2015 Agent@Home Travel Summit Town Hall Addresses Major Industry Issues Travel Agent | Agent@Home Magazine | Janeen Christoff | September 18, 2015 
PHOTO: Pictured are, from left, travAlliance CEO Mark Murphy, Scott Koepf of Avoya, and Paul Wiseman of Trafalgar. (photo by Theresa Masek) 
The Town Hall was an open session between travel agent attendees; president and CEO of travAlliancemedia, Mark Murphy; Paul Wiseman, president of Trafalgar and Scott Koepf, senior vice president of sales. Any question was on the table and there were no holds barred. It was time to take the gloves off.
